Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you finally went and played your trump card, Blue-Eyes, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I won't be done in so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to my Graverobber/Resurrection of the Dead combo, Blue-Eyes belongs to {\b0}me{\b1} now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You Summoned your own Blue-Eyes and had 'em destroy each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now you're getting desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh shit! He got his Blue-Eyes back with Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:02:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Path of a True Duelist"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faced with the Blue-Eyes that has been reunited with his true master, there's not a thing you can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you {\i1}still{\i0} won't accept defeat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! Ya think I'd accept\N something like {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give up until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of my Monsters can beat a Blue-Eyes with 3000 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I had {\b0}that{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need it for times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Baby Dragon in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best he's got? Does that mean Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s run out of options?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he may still have another trick left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where the heck did Yugi run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Anzu-{\i1}chan{\i0} hasn't come back yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that it is\N unreasonable to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I ask you to save\N my little brother, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik organized the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is no way he can\N simply be forgiven for the\N countless people he has harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did it because he was\N a victim of the fate the Ishtar clan\N has endured for years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to save that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only little brother I have!\N The one I cherish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can defeat Malik's\N dark side and rescue him from himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you! Please save the boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tomb Guardians have been\N protecting the Millennium Items
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the Pharaoh's \Nforgotten memories for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for the memories I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik hates me for this same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, I'm just as responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fight him in the upcoming Final,\N I'll defeat his dark half!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save Malik from his dark curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rescue those who fell to the\N Dark Games, Mai and Bakura, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was... I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I remember is Jounouchi about to start his Duel with Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but all Jounouchi's Monsters are in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're beaten, he won't lose Life Points, but he won't be able to strike back either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like your luck\N has just about run dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whah?!\N [Sounds like "lucky"]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! He's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! Big brother's gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulverize this deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes! Attack the Falcon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strength Increasing Medicine Super Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I take 2000 points\N of damage or more,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card automatically increases my Life Points by 4000!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Jounouchi's pretty stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough persistence is one of Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s strong points!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! I won't be beaten that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This annoying bastard just doesn't know when to accept defeat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, you can't escape your eventual defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put an end\N to it all on this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that if this attack hits, I have no hope of dodging...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's tons of\N possibilities lying in my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magician, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! This is our final fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's test whether my luck's really run out or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it! Hit it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it hits, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booyah! It hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand years passes us by!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Baby Dragon on my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...evolves into the Thousand Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for {\i1}you{\i0}, Kaiba, all the Monsters on your field are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish into the thousand-year time wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So your last dying effort\N scored a hit, did it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not going to work against {\b0}me{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue-Eyes should have vanished into the time warp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to me once again, my Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By {\i1}my{\i0} side!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activated\N Sub-Space Matter Transfer Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card transfers one Monster on my field to a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call it\N another dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my big brother for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! He almost had this won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you to defeat me relying on luck with that Gamble Deck of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I expected\N from you, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still refuse to accept your loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I meant that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, you're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling with strong guys makes my chest throb with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fun," you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you Dueling if you don't think it's fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mediocre deadbeat like you could {\i1}never{\i0} understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Duel in order to win and obtain everything I've ever wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is my {\i1}everything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya know, there's no way I {\i1}could{\i0} understand any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any cards left to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we {\i1}end{\i0} this farce...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding this\N Thunder Dragon from my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am able to add two more Thunder Dragons from my deck to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Magic Card, Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse together my\N two Thunder Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Headed Thunder Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Quick Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It allows Fusion Monsters to attack on the same turn they are Summoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I seem fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not remembering what happened\N creeps me out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me, why would\N Malik go after Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not sure about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, how's the Duel with\N Jounouchi and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be settling it\N any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Headed Thunder Dragon,\N attack Thousand Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave it your all Jounouchi, but you're still no match for big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Challenging someone to a Duel\N knowing they were going to win\N from the start was frivolous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear the howl\N of a loser dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I just lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only for the time being!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these days\N I'm gonna beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I'll fight you\N as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I lose\N to you, I'll stand back up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my path to\N becoming a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess death really {\i1}is{\i0} the only\N thing that can cure stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that, ya jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Le'go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s\N final match is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Yugi and Anzu went on ahead without even watching the end of my fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! What heartless people they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be sure to tell 'em that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Battle City is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have the Final...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no longer any meaning in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe Yugi can defeat\N Malik's Ra Deck, even after having\N won a second God Card from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... The probability is very low.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how strong the\N hidden powers within Ra are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all of this no longer has\N anything to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really any of my business, regardless of which one of them ends up winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for Yugi to win, Seto,\N he needs your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you\N going on about {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your ridiculous occult garbage\N give you another "revelation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pert kertu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've read it, have you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, have you translated\N the meaning behind the carvings\N on that stone slab palette?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 3,000 year old palette discovered\N in the Pharaoh's mortuary temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bears a prayer for the dead in Hieratic\N writing, known as the {\i1}pert kertu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dedication to the late Pharaoh, signed by his "true friend".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, what nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words, that proof of friendship,\N were left to the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by none other than\N the second being carved on\N the palette, the priest himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The corpse sinks to the floor."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The vessel becomes sand,\N becomes dust..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even the brightest gold,\N even the sharpest sword..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...is wrapped in the sheath of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Woe to the Pharaoh,\N for his body lacks even his name..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Time is a battlefield of souls."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I cry the song of battle,\N the song of a friend..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To the place far away where\N souls meet... Guide me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say, Ishizu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in some words\N inscribed on a 3,000 year old relic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... The God Cards {\i1}guided{\i0}\N you to start Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to put an {\i1}end{\i0} to these battles\N atop the Duel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your battle with the soul of your {\i1}friend{\i0},\N the Pharaoh, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Pharaoh, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a load of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to regret it if you don't stop\N muttering this annoying gibberish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, this Duel Tower you built\N is the place where souls meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}sanctuary of battle{\i0}\N built by your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sanctuary" my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That very same Duel Tower\N represents my hatred for Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was supposed to become\N the Duel King {\i1}atop{\i0} it and prove\N that I'm better than it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all {\i1}meaningless{\i0} now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll sink this place to the bottom of the sea with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, activate the detonator's time\N switch in the underground facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother... Just because you're angry\N and hateful because of how it\N was for us while growing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to make\N Yugi and the others suffer because of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met them,\N I {\i1}hated{\i0} them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they fought hard\N for me on Pegasus's island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they rescued me when\N I was captured by the Ghouls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They viewed me as one of their\N friends and tried to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think what Yugi\N and Jounouchi said was true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monsters drawn on the cards \Nwe Duelists wield in battle aren't\N the {\b0}only{\b1} demons in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The anger in our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our worst enemies are {\b0}inside{\b1} us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only when you overcome all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...can you walk the road to\N becoming a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's just what I expected\N from you, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still refuse to accept your loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I meant that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, you're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dueling with strong guys makes my chest throb with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to think\N like that before as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You enjoyed games from the\N bottom of your heart back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved the smile you used\N to show me back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I want you to\N promise me, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That when this Duel Tower sinks,\N you'll forget all about your hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go back to the old brother\N I knew before all of this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will I be able to let go of my hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I sink \Nthis Duel Tower into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Is your Duel over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're really mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning me in the middle\N of my Duel like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have you watching\N this dummy lose when your important\N final match is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? So Jounouchi lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did put up a pretty good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was still\N no match for Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You shouldn't be talkin',\N since you weren't even there\N to see my brave fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew {\i1}without{\i0} watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon guys! I'll remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I look forward to this, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Ultimate Dark Game\N awaits us in our Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will {\b0}tear you apart{\b1} and give you\N a taste of the pleasures of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this bastard is more dangerous\N than any one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a freak who likes torturing his\N opponents before defeating them\N in his Duels, and he enjoys it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like he did to Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I was stronger, I might have\N been able to save Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat Malik and save Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will! For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi probably thinks he's got the\N advantage since he beat Kaiba\N and won his God Card..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they are {\b0}worthless{\b1} against my Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One Turn Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can destroy you in\N an instant if I choose to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi has about a 3% chance\N of victory against Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One Turn Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other gods don't even {\i1}compare{\i0}\N to the hidden powers of Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A key card that I own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only card that can\N seal the power of Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}with{\i0} the card in Yugi's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his chances will only go up\N to about 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Duel Arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This should be entertaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a game with\N only a 20% chance of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said, "I won through the\N power of my friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, I'll take this card, with the\N little possibility is holds of winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Yugi, I'll entrust it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you perform a miracle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no such {\b0}thing{\b1} as miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no such {\b0}thing{\b1}\N as the power of a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your {\b0}defeat{\b1}\N will be the proof of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} gave Yugi a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi places the card in his deck without a moment's hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the final match of the Battle City Tournament begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way to fight against the hidden abilities of Malik's God Card, the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! You can do it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Final: Yugi VS Malik"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:23:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
